metadata.name: Honey Badger #1
metadata.description: The Honey Badgers collection is the second collection in the Degenz Den metaverse. They are meant to accompany the Genesis collection as a reward for holding your Hyenas.  Honey Badgers are full members of the Degenz Den metaverse and will get access to all of the members-only areas, including the cryptovoxels space and discord channels. Honey Badger holders will also receive cryptovoxels wearables and are granted full commercial rights to their respective NFTs.
